TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT INV.REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY, INV.SALES_ORDER_KEY, INV.SALES_ORDER_LINE_KEY, INV.PRODUCT_KEY, INV.AR_TRX_KEY, INV.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY, INV.BK_AR_TRX_LINE_GL_DISTRIB_KEY, INV.END_CUSTOMER_KEY, INV.BILL_TO_CUSTOMER_KEY, INV.SHIP_TO_CUSTOMER_KEY, INV.SOLD_TO_CUSTOMER_KEY, INV.SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, INV.DIRECT_CORP_ADJUSTMENT_KEY, INV.GENERAL_LEDGER_ACCOUNT_KEY, INV.SALES_REP_NUMBER, INV.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT, INV.BK_SALES_ADJ_LINE_NUMBER_INT, INV.BK_SALES_ADJ_NUMBER_INT, INV.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT, INV.DD_BK_FINANCIAL_ACCOUNT_CD, INV.DD_GL_DATETIME, INV.DD_BK_TRXL_CURRENCY_CD, INV.BK_ORDER_TYPE_NAME, INV.DV_FISCAL_DT, INV.DD_FUNCTIONAL_CURRENCY_CD, INV.DD_BK_AR_TRX_TYPE_CD, INV.DD_BK_DIRECT_CORP_ADJ_TYPE_CD, INV.DD_SERVICE_TYPE_CD, INV.BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CD, INV.AR_TRX_DATETIME, INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD, INV.DV_FORWARD_REVERSE_CD, INV.DV_CORPORATE_REVENUE_FLG, INV.DV_IC_REVENUE_FLG, INV.DV_CHARGES_FLG, INV.DV_MISC_FLG, INV.DV_SERVICE_FLG, INV.DV_INTERNATIONAL_DEMO_FLG, INV.DV_REPLACEMENT_DEMO_FLG, INV.DV_REVENUE_FLG, INV.DV_COMP_US_NET_PRICE_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_NET_LIST_PRICE_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_GROSS_LIST_PRICE_AM, INV.DV_COMP_US_NET_COST_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_GROSS_REV_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_NET_REV_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_2TIER_CMDM_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_GROSS_COST_AMT, INV.DV_COMP_US_STANDARD_PRICE_AMT, INV.DD_EXTENDED_NET_QTY, INV.DD_EXTENDED_GROSS_QTY, INV.EDW_CREATE_USER, INV.EDW_CREATE_DATETIME, INV.EDW_UPDATE_USER, INV.EDW_UPDATE_DATETIME, 'UNK' BK_ADJUSTMENT_TYPE_CD , 'UNK' BK_REVENUE_OR_COGS_TYPE_CD , CAST(INV.DD_GL_DATETIME as DATE) GL_DT, NULL BK_SS_CD , 0 DV_EXTENDED_QTY , 0 GL_DISTRIB_FUNCTIONAL_AMT , 0 GL_DISTRIB_TRANSACTIONAL_AMT , NULL OPERATING_UNIT_NAME_CD , NULL ACCOUNT_CLASS_CD , NULL TRANSACTION_TYPE_CATEGORY_CD , NULL WAREHOUSE_INVENTORY_ORG_KEY , CASE WHEN INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD='POS' THEN NPTL.TRANSACTION_DATE ELSE INV.DV_FISCAL_DT END TRANSACTION_DT, NULL GL_POSTED_DTM ,
RANDOM(1000000,1001800)*-1 AS RAE_ADJUSTMENT_SCHEDULE_LN_KEY, 0 DV_COMP_FUNC_NET_PRICE_AMT , 0 DV_COMP_FUNC_GROSS_REV_AMT , 0 DV_COMP_FUNC_NET_REV_AMT , 0 SPLIT_PCT , 'UNK' BK_COMPANY_CODE , 'UNK' BK_ISO_COUNTRY_CODE , 'N' DV_2T_DISTI_REVENUE_FLG , -999 AS REVENUE_TRANSFER_KEY , INV.DV_SALES_ORDER_LINE_KEY AS DV_SALES_ORDER_LINE_KEY, INV.SK_OFFER_ATTRIBUTION_ID_INT AS SK_OFFER_ATTRIBUTION_ID_INT, INV.DV_PRODUCT_KEY AS DV_PRODUCT_KEY, INV.DV_ATTRIBUTION_CD AS DV_ATTRIBUTION_CD, COALESCE(CASE WHEN (ABT.BK_BATCH_SOURCE_NAME IN ('SALES ADJUSTMENTS-WEBEX', 'WEBEX','ICMS-ADJ-WEBEX' ) OR ABT.BK_BATCH_SOURCE_NAME LIKE ANY('XAAS%','ICMS-XAAS%','CSP-MARKETPLACE'))
THEN SO.BK_DEAL_ID ELSE NSO. BK_DEAL_ID END ,'UNKNOWN') DV_ERP_DEAL_ID, COALESCE(CASE WHEN (ABT.BK_BATCH_SOURCE_NAME IN ('SALES ADJUSTMENTS-WEBEX', 'WEBEX','ICMS-ADJ-WEBEX' ) OR ABT.BK_BATCH_SOURCE_NAME LIKE ANY('XAAS%','ICMS-XAAS%','CSP-MARKETPLACE'))
THEN SO.BK_SALES_CHANNEL_CODE ELSE NSO. BK_SALES_CHANNEL_CODE END ,'UNKNOWN') BK_SALES_CHANNEL_CD, 'N' DV_FMV_FLG , TRANSACTION_TYPE_CATEGORY_CD DV_TRANS_TYPE_CATEGORY_CD, 0 DV_SHIPPED_REVENUE_AMT, 0 DV_FUNC_SHIPPED_REVENUE_AMT
,INV.BK_BOOKING_POS_TRX_ID_INT ,INV.DSV_FLG
,INV.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY AS DV_AR_TRX_LINE_KEY ,-999 AS XAAS_OFFER_ATRBTN_REV_LINE_KEY ,'UNK' BK_SUBINVENTORY_NAME ,'N' XCAT_FLG ,'UNK' BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,'N' RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,'N' ELA_FLG , -999 ADJSMT_RBT_TRX_LIN_GL_DIST_KEY ,0 DV_COMP_US_NET_PURC_ADJ_AMT ,'UNK' DV_RECURRING_OFFER_CD ,INV.POB_TYPE_CD ,'N' NRS_TRANSITION_FLG ,'N' DV_PRODUCT_SUBSCRIPTION_FLG ,INV.SK_RTR_ATTRIBUTION_ID ,INV.SALES_MOTION_CD ,INV.DV_TRANSACTION_KEY FROM $$STGDB.WK_INV_REV_MEASURE_POS_SMR INV LEFT OUTER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LINE NPTL ON ( NPTL.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT =INV.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT )
INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_ORDER NSO ON INV.SALES_ORDER_KEY=NSO.SALES_ORDER_KEY INNER JOIN $$FINLGLVWDB.N_AR_TRX_LINE ARTL ON INV.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY=ARTL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY INNER JOIN $$FINLGLVWDB.N_AR_TRX ART ON ART.AR_TRX_KEY=ARTL.AR_TRX_KEY LEFT OUTER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_ORDER_LINE SOL ON ARTL.RU_EXAAS_SUBSCRIPTION_SOL_KEY = SOL.SALES_ORDER_LINE_KEY LEFT OUTER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_ORDER SO ON SOL.SALES_ORDER_KEY=SO.SALES_ORDER_KEY INNER JOIN $$FINLGLVWDB.N_AR_BATCH_SOURCE ABT ON ABT.AR_BATCH_SOURCE_KEY=ART.AR_BATCH_SOURCE_KEY
